a new york toymaker is recalling 7600 bead 
coaster toys because the wooden beads may become detached and 
pose a fatal choking hazard to young children 
the three metal blue yellow and red wires of the toys form a 
hill and valley rollercoaster shaped vertical field attached to a 
wooden base to create what a spokeswoman for the consumer product 
