overdue parker said in a telephone interview from reston va 
the policy which has been approved in principle by school 
officials lists several behaviors that would qualify as sexual 
harassment among them staring or leering with sexual overtones 
spreading sexual gossip making unwanted sexual comments exerting 
pressure for sexual activity and making unwanted physical contact 
of a sexual nature 
