the strange odyssey is part of the steppedup battle against the 
weed considered one of north dakotas most persistent pests 
hirsch works for the animal and plant health inspection service 
of the us department of agriculture which is importing the 
beetles in the hope they will ravage the spurge infesting 12 
million acres across the state 
north dakota has north americas worst infestation of the tall 
weed with greenyellow flowers that was brought over from europe in 
