uaw ford was running as much as 20 percent over factory capacity 
in order to deal with surging car and truck demand sales since 
then have weakened 
the union has complained that physical and psychological burdens 
on employees can result from such overwork extensive overtime also 
indicates the companys hourly work force is too small bieber said 
