in the unusual position of defending his sometimeadversary 
one should not undercut the ability of the head of an 
independent agency to express disagreement breeden said 
asked about a possible tax on securities transactions that white 
house budget experts have reportedly been kicking around breeden 
said i think we have to be extraordinarily careful in creating 
taxes on capital formation 
we have to be very careful that we do not take steps which 
drive trade from our shores he said 
outside the hearing room breeden said he has not been privy to 
